    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Rinse your<strong> quinoa</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>quinoa</strong> to a large pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for an initial 6-7 min</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> Tenderstem broccoli </strong>into thirds</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>beetroot</strong> in a colander over the sink</p><p>Chop the<strong> drained beetroot</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>After the initial 6-7 min, add the<strong> chopped Tenderstem </strong>to the quinoa pot</p><p>Cook for a final 3-4 min or until the broccoli is tender with a slight bite, and all the quinoa is tender</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>traditional</strong> <strong>Italian pesto</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>pesto dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>cooked quinoa & broccoli</strong> and rinse under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Drain and return to the pot</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained lentils</strong> to the pot with the <strong>chopped beetroot</strong>,<strong> cashews</strong> and <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>pesto dressing </strong>(you'll use the rest later) and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>grain salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/goats-cheese-and-beetroot-grain-bowl-with-pesto-dressing/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>grain salad</strong> and crumble your<strong> goats' cheese</strong> all over</p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>reserved pesto dressing </strong>and garnish with your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
